    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tumbles (Previously Silk Soar) is a Physics Flinging, Rage Bringing Narrative 2D Platformer (Foddian), where you take on life as a newborn caterpillar attempting to meet the challenges of flinging yourself from the rainforest floor to the top of the canopy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/df3a73dedec32888b86de45348c79f51.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/df3a73dedec32888b86de45348c79f51.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/df3a73dedec32888b86de45348c79f51.mp4?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/93d755e131a7b11e87278d351f474a35.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=617 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/93d755e131a7b11e87278d351f474a35.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launch your caterpillar around using a catapult-like motion to bounce off walls and flowers, be pushed by the wind, slide across wet leaves and avoid obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/094a3b13f17998011df170e9ad2b8e11.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/094a3b13f17998011df170e9ad2b8e11.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/094a3b13f17998011df170e9ad2b8e11.mp4?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/aefde95bc7444ddd48ff129d4c5c72a6.avif?t=1768313354\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you reach higher into the canopy you will face more difficult jumps and a variety of obstacles to go further through the layers of the rainforest in search of the top of the canopy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/7c1caed6f2f61d9123a3f0ea6677f034.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/7c1caed6f2f61d9123a3f0ea6677f034.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/7c1caed6f2f61d9123a3f0ea6677f034.mp4?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/4b18d9aa91e64ff89c8f84a17b23e37c.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=617 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/4b18d9aa91e64ff89c8f84a17b23e37c.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the poetic narrative of the struggles of reaching from the depths of darkness in search of freedom and light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/433a5a1e5d70137fa607bd3254ce1032.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/433a5a1e5d70137fa607bd3254ce1032.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/433a5a1e5d70137fa607bd3254ce1032.mp4?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/533dcd6c19d2b5d578c5aabccc166d7c.poster.avif?t=1768313354\" width=617 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277320/extras/533dcd6c19d2b5d578c5aabccc166d7c.webm?t=1768313354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you choose to build your cocoon there is an increasing chance of evolutions affecting your next caterpillar. Will you be a different colour, have a more bouncy body, or have tunnel vision? What combinations will you have and will they help or hinder your next climb? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Tumbles, every climb can bring you further through the climb you have faced before or challenge you with a combination of evolutions. Will you make it out from the forest floor and into the light or will this climb be cut short as another cocoon in the darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you make it to freedom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
